OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773151900
OL,3,CLong-standing construction company
OL,4,Ccollapses with 25 job losses
OL,6,FThe construction company SGB Hire
OL,7,FChannel Islands has collapsed.
OL,9,FThe business had served Jersey and
OL,10,FGuernsey for more than half a century,
OL,11,Fafter beginning operations in 1968.
OL,13,FIt has now ceased trading with
OL,14,Fimmediate effect, as the firm
OL,15,Fconfirmed that 25 people have lost
OL,16,Ftheir jobs.
OL,18,FSGB Hire Channel Islands was closed
OL,19,Fafter a decision by the company's UK
OL,20,Fowner, Brand Safway.
