OL,3,CLong-standing construction company
OL,4,Ccollapses with 25 job losses
OL,6,FA spokesperson has told ITV Channel
OL,7,Fthat the business will be prioritising
OL,8,Fsupport for affected workers.
OL,10,FThe firm described itself as "one of
OL,11,Fthe Channel Islands' only fully
OL,12,Fintegrated suppliers", offering a
OL,13,Frange of services from equipment hire
OL,14,Ffor events to landscaping machinery
OL,15,Fand tools.
