OL,3,CLong-standing construction company
OL,4,Ccollapses with 25 job losses
OL,6,FIn a statement, Adrian De Gruchy,
OL,7,FChairman of the Jersey Construction
OL,8,FCouncil, says they "wish to recognise
OL,9,Fthe impact on all parties affected,
OL,10,Fincluding the directors, employees,
OL,11,Fclients, subcontractors and
OL,12,Fsuppliers".
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
